msgid "Soldier's bombs can hit through walls."
msgstr "士兵炸弹能透过墙壁造成伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:133
msgid ""
"Ninja's slash deals 9 damage by default. One more pistol shot will kill an "
"infected with no armor."
msgstr "忍者的斩击默认造成 9 点伤害。再用手枪射击一次就能击杀没有盾的感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:134
msgid ""
"Ninja with a single strength upgrade can kill an armorless infected with a "
"single slash."
msgstr "具有强度升级的忍者用一次斩击就能击杀没有盾的感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:135
msgid ""
"Ninja doesn't need to directly kill their target. An assist with a laser "
"blind or grenade stun will still grant the rewards."
msgstr ""
"忍者不一定需要直接击杀目标。通过激光致盲或者榴弹冰冻协助队友击杀目标仍能获得"
"奖励。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:136
