"Slug can heal itself and allies over time up to {int:MaxHP} HP with its "
"slime."
msgstr "鼻涕虫和它的队友能站在黏液里来回血（最多 {int:MaxHP} 点）。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:159
msgid ""
"Slug can hold down the \"fire\" button to automatically spread slime. The "
"hammer swings won't hurt humans this way though."
msgstr "鼻涕虫能长按开火键来自动散播黏液。这种情况下锤子不会锤到人类。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:160
msgid "Voodoo can unfreeze an Undead while in Spirit mode."
msgstr "巫毒者可以在灵魂状态解冻一名不死族。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:161
msgid "Witch can spawn the infected through narrow walls."
msgstr "女巫能让感染者透过窄墙出生。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:162
msgid ""
"Undead can be removed from a game by throwing it into kill tiles or reviving "
"it as a Medic."
msgstr "通过把不死族扔进刺里或者作为医生治疗它可以消灭一个不死族。"

